Review Text: I have ordered nuts overload it was out of stock and got strawberry ice cream in return but the ice cream was nice and enjoyed the ice cream
Ordered a Belgium Dark Chocolate. That was the worst shit that I have tasted as an ice cream. The worst I must say!! Never ordering from here again!
Ice cream was too sweet, and they also delivered wrong one. Instead of full size Death By Chocolate, i got cups of some random flavour. Had to throw as it was too sweet. Will never order from here
